collections.name: MetaPaws Matter
collections.description:
MetaPaws Matter is an ERC-721 NFT collection dedicated to transforming the lives of stray and abandoned cats. Each NFT features cat-inspired artwork, inspired by the grace and charm of our feline companions. By owning a Metapaws Matter NFT, you're joining a mission to create a better world for cats.
 
Utility and Purpose: 

1) A portion of every sale funds food, shelter and medical care for cats in in need.

2) Exclusive Perks for holders, including access to upcoming community events and charity auctions, future collections and merchandise.

3) Participate in charity voting to choose supported organizations.

4) Unlock future benefits, including metaverse integrations and token-gated rewards. 

Every NFT represents hope and love for cats everywhere, proving that MetaPaws Matter - both virtually and in the real World.
